    "Sentences with a total of 𝑝 words are fed into the model, and BERT excites the input text into a collection of 𝑛 tokens.",
    "Each token will be subjected to a conversion process that yields a numeric vector of 768 dimensions.",
    "The output produced by BERT is a 768-dimensional vector, which functions as a contextualized representation for every character.",
    "The vectors are arranged in a matrix of dimensions 𝑛×768.",
    "The convolutional layer applies a filter to the 𝑛×768 matrix derived from BERT, partitioning it and generating a vector output with dimensions 𝑛-𝑠+1."
